o}}</ref>。

== 结构 ==
内耳的核心部分为[[骨迷路|骨迷路]]，由[[耳蜗|耳蜗]]和[[前庭系统|前庭系统]]组成。骨迷路内有[[膜迷路|膜迷路]]，膜迷路中含有[[内淋巴|内淋巴]]，而外淋巴包裹膜迷路（介于骨迷路和膜迷路之间），起保护作用<ref>{{Cite web|title=Membranous Labyrinth - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/membranous-labyrinth|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Membranous labyrinth {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/membranous-labyrinth?lang=us|accessdate=2021-03-11|last=Hacking|first=Craig|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429054558/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/membranous-labyrinth?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。骨迷路中的外淋巴液与[[蛛網膜|蛛网膜]]下腔的[[脑脊液|脑脊液]]通过{{link-en|外淋巴管|Perilymphatic duct}}相连<ref>{{cite book|author=Blumenfeld, Hal|title=Neuroanatomy through Clinical Cases second edition|url=https://archive.org/details/neuroanatomythro0000blum|publisher=Sinauer Associates, Inc.|year=2010}}</ref>。

== 成分及功能 ==
外淋巴和内淋巴液中特有的离子成分可调节听觉[[毛细胞|毛细胞]]的电化学冲动。内淋巴液比外淋巴液的[[电势差|电势]]高出80-90[[毫伏|毫伏]]，这是因为内淋巴液含有更高浓度的钾离子而外淋巴液含有更高浓度的钠离子，这被称为{{link-en|耳蜗内电位|Endocochlear potential}}<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Endolymph and Perilymph - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/endolymph-and-perilymph|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Ion transport in guinea pig cochlea. I. Potassium and sodium transport|journal=[[Acta_Otolaryngol|Acta Otolaryngol]]|issue=1–2|doi=10.3109/00016487809124717|year=1978|volume=86|pages=22–34|pmid=696294|vauthors=Konishi T, Hamrick PE, Walsh PJ}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Supporting sensory transduction: cochlear fluid homeostasis and the endocochlear potential|last=Wangemann|first=Philine|date=2006-10-01|journal=The Journal of Physiology|issue=Pt 1|doi=10.1113/jphysiol.2006.112888|volume=576|pages=11–21|issn=0022-3751|pmc=1995626|pmid=16857713}}</ref>。

此外，外淋巴中含有大量[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]，对[[代谢|代谢]]和[[免疫反應|免疫反应]]起到重要作用<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The proteome of perilymph in patients with vestibular schwannoma. A possibility to identify biomarkers for tumor associated hearing loss?|first1=Jesper|last2=Laurell|first2=Göran|date=2018|journal=PLOS ONE|issue=6|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0198442|volume=13|pages=e0198442|bibcode=2018PLoSO..1398442E|issn=1932-6203|pmc=5983529|pmid=29856847|last3=Rask-Andersen|first3=Helge|last4=Bergquist|first4=Jonas|last5=Eriksson|first5=Per Olof|last1=Edvardsson Rasmussen}}</ref>。

== 临床 ==
有研究认为[[梅尼埃病|梅尼埃病]]是内耳的[[内淋巴|内淋巴]]、外淋巴单向流动受阻造成<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Histopathology of Meniere’s disease|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5344024/|last=Cureoglu|first=Sebahattin|last2=da Costa Monsanto|first2=Rafael|date=2016-12|journal=Operative techniques in otolaryngology--head and neck surgery|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.otot.2016.10.003|volume=27|pages=194–204|issn=1043-1810|pmc=5344024|pmid=28286401|last3=Paparella|first3=Michael M.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Meniere's disease - Symptoms and causes|url=https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/menieres-disease/symptoms-causes/syc-20374910|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=Mayo Clinic|language=en|archive-date=2013-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530232848/http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/menieres-disease/DS00535/DSECTION=symptoms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

